    <item>
      <title>印尼当选总统普拉博沃将在莫斯科会见普京</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/indonesia-s-president-elect-prabowo-to-meet-putin-in-moscow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼当选总统普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 将于今天晚些时候在莫斯科会见俄罗斯领导人弗拉基米尔·普京 (Vladimir Putin)。去年，他曾推动一项和平提议，但未能成功，该提议将使俄罗斯占领乌克兰部分地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/indonesia-s-president-elect-prabowo-to-meet-putin-in-moscow</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:48:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
